    # game/sleeping.rpy:285
    old "You think of the leaders you’ve encountered, the work you’ve done for them, and the sacrifices you had to make to get on their good side. Here, in the far North, you spin the first threads of your web of connections. Yet something distorts your new beginning, a shadow that gets greater with every heartbeat. \n\nYou keep waking up, not sure if these thoughts are a dream, a memory, or a vision. You stand up, walk around, and breathe, slowly, deeply, your stomach rising and falling. "
    new ""

