    old "The monstrous shouts wake you up. The night is bright, and from the window of the tavern, you have a good look at the yard. \n\nA few massive dragonlings are exploring the courtyard, knocking over wooden tools with their tails, putting their noses into buckets and underneath the stairs. You count five of them so far, but you can’t see the entire area at once. \n\nOne of them spots your look, and moves closer. Still, it doesn’t try to climb to the door - maybe it’s experienced enough to know it won’t get through. "
    new ""

